  "title": "Process Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist or lead material movement from AMS to the Pilot Plant/PRL, including bulk material withdrawal, staging, transfer, receiving, warehousing, and issuance to manufacturing.</li><li>Execute SAP transactions related to material movements.</li><li>Perform weighing and dispensing activities in accordance with requirements.</li><li>Stage and issue materials to the operations team based on the production plan.</li><li>Monitor warehouse supplies to support uninterrupted operations.</li><li>Ensure proper material rotation following FIFO/FEFO principles.</li><li>Maintain accurate inventory through routine physical counts.</li><li>Support preparation and shipment of finished products for their intended use.</li><li>Maintain proper housekeeping and organize storage areas by managing floor space, monitoring storage conditions, and complying with GMP standards.</li><li>Comply with safety and quality standards </li><li>Perform weighing and dispensing activities for APP and PRL operations.</li></ul>",
